# tkv2 — theme as CSS custom properties

Slice `tkv2-theme-css-vars` of `specs/ssc-toolkit-v2.md`: one `Theme` value
drives both the toolkit and any hand-kept CSS via `var(--ssc-*)`.

[Theme, defaultTheme, darkTheme, cssVariables](std/ui/theme.ssc)

```scalascript
val css = cssVariables(defaultTheme)
println(css.startsWith(":root {"))
println(css.contains("--ssc-color-primary: #2563eb;"))
println(css.contains("--ssc-space-md: 16px;"))
println(css.contains("--ssc-radius-full: "))
println(css.endsWith("}"))

val dark = cssVariables(darkTheme)
println(dark != css)
println(dark.contains("--ssc-color-primary: "))
```
